@startuml test-strategy
title Estrategia de pruebas — CircleGuard (HU-09)\nPirámide de tests + tareas Gradle + dependencias por nivel

skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor<<unit>>        #C8E6C9
  BackgroundColor<<integration>> #FFE0B2
  BackgroundColor<<e2e>>         #FFCDD2
  BackgroundColor<<task>>        #BBDEFB
  BorderColor                    #424242
  FontStyle                      bold
}

' --- Capa Unitaria ---
rectangle "Unit tests\n(JUnit 5 + Mockito + MockMvc slice)" as Unit <<unit>> {
  rectangle "auth: 83.2%" as U1
  rectangle "dashboard: 89.7%" as U2
  rectangle "file: 88.9%" as U3
  rectangle "form: 92.0%" as U4
  rectangle "gateway: 88.9%" as U5
  rectangle "identity: 83.8%" as U6
  rectangle "notification: 75.8% (gap doc.)" as U7
  rectangle "promotion: 81.5%" as U8
}

' --- Capa Integración ---
rectangle "Integration tests\n@Tag(\"integration\")\nTestcontainers + EmbeddedKafka + WebMvc" as Int <<integration>> {
  rectangle "AuthIdentityClient\n(MockServerContainer)" as I1
  rectangle "SurveyKafkaPublish\n(@EmbeddedKafka)" as I2
  rectangle "StatusChangeNotification\n(@EmbeddedKafka)" as I3
  rectangle "DashboardPromotionClient\n(@MockBean)" as I4
  rectangle "IdentityMapping\n(@WebMvcTest + Security)" as I5
  rectangle "SurveyListenerToService\n(@EmbeddedKafka)" as I6
}

' --- Capa E2E ---
rectangle "E2E tests\n@Tag(\"e2e\")\nREST Assured contra stack desplegado" as E2E <<e2e>> {
  rectangle "CertificateValidationFlow" as E1
  rectangle "DashboardStatsFlow" as E2
  rectangle "HealthSurveyFlow" as E3
  rectangle "IdentityMappingFlow" as E4
}

' --- Tasks Gradle ---
rectangle "gradlew test\n(default, excluye integration + e2e)" as TaskUnit <<task>>
rectangle "gradlew integrationTest\n(requiere Docker para Testcontainers)" as TaskInt <<task>>
rectangle ":tests:e2e:e2eTest\n(requiere stack desplegado)" as TaskE2E <<task>>
rectangle "jacocoTestReport\n(HTML + XML, suma exec de test + integrationTest)" as Jacoco <<task>>

' --- Relaciones ---
Unit ..> TaskUnit : ejecutado por
Int  ..> TaskInt  : ejecutado por
E2E  ..> TaskE2E  : ejecutado por

TaskUnit -> Jacoco : finalizedBy
TaskInt  -> Jacoco : finalizedBy

' --- Notas explicativas ---
note right of Unit
  Sin Docker, sin red, sin stack.
  Corre en laptop / CI agent local.
  Cubre lógica pura aislada.
  Floor JaCoCo: 80% líneas
  (regla registrada, no atada a check
   todavía — notification gap doc.)
end note

note right of Int
  Requiere Docker en el agent.
  AuthIdentityClient usa MockServerContainer real,
  los Kafka heredados usan @EmbeddedKafka in-process.
  Exclusión: estos NO corren en `gradlew test`.
end note

note right of E2E
  CI contra AKS de stage.
  Requiere: 8 servicios desplegados,
  Postgres + Kafka + Neo4j + LDAP + Redis,
  data seeds aplicados.
  Pendiente de Ops (HU-09b).
end note

note bottom of Jacoco
  Excludes:
   - **/*Application.class
   - **/dto/**, **/model/**
   - **/config/**, **/event/**
   - **/exception/**, **/SecurityConfig.class
  Reporte HTML: services/<svc>/build/reports/jacoco/test/html/index.html
  Reporte XML para SonarQube: jacocoTestReport.xml
end note

@enduml
